room_title: Escape room "The Last Escape" by Adventures by Appointment in Tacoma
room_description:
The Last Escape is a mystery, a story of love and revenge and of course a theatrically engaging escape room. It will challenge you and your friends to cooperate, communicate and solve your way out of imprisonment by the powerful family that owns and operates an infamous mediums parlor.
You are brought to the infamous medium's parlor to have your tarot cards. It becomes obvious that your group is not alone in the room. Your task is to set the magician's spirit free and physically escape the room yourselves.
